div.p: Be a part of the tech company that’s a part of everything

Technology is a force for good. It connects us and changes how we live, work, and play. At the heart of it all is ASML. Most of the electronic devices you use daily are only possible because of our lithography systems.
Working at ASML is unlike working at any other company - even other high-tech companies. It's more extreme and more inspiring, no matter the field you're in.
That’s because we push the boundaries of what’s physically possible. Every field of technology stretched to its limits and beyond.
ASML offers opportunities for students and graduates in practically every technical field.
Our engineers develop skills that pave the way for rapid professional and personal growth, as well as a promising future solving complex problems.
Explore our internships, co-op programs and graduation assignments for students in the Netherlands and the United States.
Get support for your future – see the available scholarships in the Netherlands and the US.
Explore our career events and workshops for PhD students and graduates in the Netherlands and the US.
Learn about our career events held around the world, where you get to know ASML as an employer.
ASML is headquartered in Veldhoven amid a thriving ecosystem of high-tech companies. Our headquarters is home to more than half of all our employees.
With 14 customer support sites, two factories, and three R&D centers, our US locations service Intel and other customers and contribute to our holistic product portfolio.

We have the largest ASML manufacturing site in Asia as well as two training centers, play an essential role in the rapidly growing e-beam market, and work closely with TSMC and major semiconductor fabs.
Our teams in South Korea work closely with Samsung and other customers and have five locations that include a global distribution center and 4 training centers.
We support both global big-name customers and fast-growing local customers with 12 customer support sites, two R&D centers, and one training center.
Japan is home to tech giants and major semiconductor players, with whom ASML collaborates closely. You can help to advance technology – and your career.

Discover what it’s like to work at ASML. Dive into this interactive section to learn about compensation and benefits, well-being, volunteering and giving back to our communities, employee networks and sports clubs, exciting events, and learning and development.
Read our most frequently asked questions about applying for a job at ASML.

template.h2: Applying for a job at ASML

dt.click: slotProps.toggleItem('{58EACD08-4325-4C95-8A43-8E54789503EB}','How do I apply for a job at ASML?')
dt.keyup.enter: slotProps.toggleItem('{58EACD08-4325-4C95-8A43-8E54789503EB}', 'How do I apply for a job at ASML?')
dt.h3: How do I apply for a job at ASML?

dd.div: Use the ASML job search to find a position that matches your skill set. Click the "Apply now" button on any open job listing at ASML, which will direct you to the ASML career portal. From there, you can fill out the form and submit your application. We are unable to accept job applications submitted any other way, such as via email.

dt.click: slotProps.toggleItem('{6A3B6F88-8108-4305-B157-E88CB0A632CA}','Who will review my job application?')
dt.keyup.enter: slotProps.toggleItem('{6A3B6F88-8108-4305-B157-E88CB0A632CA}', 'Who will review my job application?')
dt.h3: Who will review my job application?

dd.div: A recruitment specialist in the department of the open position will review your resume and cover letter.

dt.click: slotProps.toggleItem('{281843A2-6023-4245-BF51-58234BEAFC59}','When will I hear back after I apply for a job at ASML?')
dt.keyup.enter: slotProps.toggleItem('{281843A2-6023-4245-BF51-58234BEAFC59}', 'When will I hear back after I apply for a job at ASML?')
dt.h3: When will I hear back after I apply for a job at ASML?

dd.div: An ASML recruiter will contact you within two weeks if we have questions about your application or if we would like to schedule an interview.

dt.click: slotProps.toggleItem('{EC892FA0-C631-4682-904F-1D181E1B0149}','Until when can I apply for a job listing that does not have an expiration date?')
dt.keyup.enter: slotProps.toggleItem('{EC892FA0-C631-4682-904F-1D181E1B0149}', 'Until when can I apply for a job listing that does not have an expiration date?')
dt.h3: Until when can I apply for a job listing that does not have an expiration date?

dd.div: We encourage you to apply as soon as possible, as the job listing expiration date depends on the number of qualified applicants.

dt.click: slotProps.toggleItem('{CB42500F-F543-461F-93CC-236C801CEE7F}','Can I apply for more than one job at ASML?')
dt.keyup.enter: slotProps.toggleItem('{CB42500F-F543-461F-93CC-236C801CEE7F}', 'Can I apply for more than one job at ASML?')
dt.h3: Can I apply for more than one job at ASML?

dd.div: Yes, but we encourage you to only apply for jobs that match your background and experience. If you are invited for the second round of interviews for both positions, you will need to choose with which position you would like to proceed.

dt.click: slotProps.toggleItem('{4E0E8CB1-1FC3-4B54-AA10-AEA6A7DCB610}','What is the status of my job application?')
dt.keyup.enter: slotProps.toggleItem('{4E0E8CB1-1FC3-4B54-AA10-AEA6A7DCB610}', 'What is the status of my job application?')
dt.h3: What is the status of my job application?

div.p: After you have filled out the online application for a job at ASML, you will see an option to create a personal profile in the career portal. After creating a profile, you can log in and view the status of your job application.

dt.click: slotProps.toggleItem('{92DC0F41-23F7-4E44-93E8-219EAC7DA45A}','What does it mean if my application status is "closed"?')
dt.keyup.enter: slotProps.toggleItem('{92DC0F41-23F7-4E44-93E8-219EAC7DA45A}', 'What does it mean if my application status is "closed"?')
dt.h3: What does it mean if my application status is "closed"?

dd.div: If your application status appears as "closed", it means that you were not selected to proceed to the next step of the hiring process. We encourage you to search for a job at ASML that matches your skill set and apply again.

dt.click: slotProps.toggleItem('{0880B822-F4F4-4A65-87AB-60956D674F29}','What is the main language spoken at ASML?')
dt.keyup.enter: slotProps.toggleItem('{0880B822-F4F4-4A65-87AB-60956D674F29}', 'What is the main language spoken at ASML?')
dt.h3: What is the main language spoken at ASML?

div.p: Our company’s main language is English. We are proudly culturally diverse, with 120 different nationalities working together as one.

dt.click: slotProps.toggleItem('{A9FB3FB1-1F1F-4090-A6C8-4BD66F8D7176}','Can I visit ASML before I apply for a job?')
dt.keyup.enter: slotProps.toggleItem('{A9FB3FB1-1F1F-4090-A6C8-4BD66F8D7176}', 'Can I visit ASML before I apply for a job?')
dt.h3: Can I visit ASML before I apply for a job?

div.p: ASML organizes several events each year for students and professionals that take place at our various locations around the world. Check out our career events to find an event that matches your interests.

dt.click: slotProps.toggleItem('{F4F2F6C1-F33C-465E-823F-34D14694DD45}','What is the ASML interview process like?')
dt.keyup.enter: slotProps.toggleItem('{F4F2F6C1-F33C-465E-823F-34D14694DD45}', 'What is the ASML interview process like?')
dt.h3: What is the ASML interview process like?

div.p: The ASML interview process will vary depending on the job you are applying for as well as which country you are applying in. Generally, however, you may have two or more interviews for a job at ASML. The first interview, which takes place with the position’s hiring manager and a member of the team, assesses your background, skills and compatibility with the team.

If you are invited for a second interview, you may be asked to complete an online assessment that should be submitted before the interview takes place. The second interview takes place with a project leader, architect or different team member. You may also be invited to a third interview with the human resources (HR) department. If all interviews are successful, you will then receive a job offer from HR.

dt.click: slotProps.toggleItem('{7B9A5BCF-2753-4A47-8D82-8F5A99B0DF7E}','When will I receive an invitation for my interview?')
dt.keyup.enter: slotProps.toggleItem('{7B9A5BCF-2753-4A47-8D82-8F5A99B0DF7E}', 'When will I receive an invitation for my interview?')
dt.h3: When will I receive an invitation for my interview?

div.p: The ASML recruitment department will send you an email that includes information about the location, date, and interviewers once the interview has been planned.

dt.click: slotProps.toggleItem('{E60A84A8-AB4F-4BB6-8454-F0AD136C6217}','I have been asked to complete an online assessment for the job I have applied for. How much time do I have to complete it?')
dt.keyup.enter: slotProps.toggleItem('{E60A84A8-AB4F-4BB6-8454-F0AD136C6217}', 'I have been asked to complete an online assessment for the job I have applied for. How much time do I have to complete it?')
dt.h3: I have been asked to complete an online assessment for the job I have applied for. How much time do I have to complete it?

dd.div: Once you have received the online assessment, we encourage you to complete it within three days. Please make sure you have completed the assessment before your interview.

dt.click: slotProps.toggleItem('{8A20E219-1DEF-484E-B438-DF5B4947F1CF}','When will I hear back after my interview?')
dt.keyup.enter: slotProps.toggleItem('{8A20E219-1DEF-484E-B438-DF5B4947F1CF}', 'When will I hear back after my interview?')
dt.h3: When will I hear back after my interview?

dd.div: It depends on the country in which you are applying for a job, but you should generally receive feedback within five working days.

dt.click: slotProps.toggleItem('{35BD794A-29E1-44E2-BACB-33FC4316FA3D}','I did not receive a QR code or online meeting link for my interview.')
dt.keyup.enter: slotProps.toggleItem('{35BD794A-29E1-44E2-BACB-33FC4316FA3D}', 'I did not receive a QR code or online meeting link for my interview.')
dt.h3: I did not receive a QR code or online meeting link for my interview.

dd.div: Please contact the recruiter that sent you the interview confirmation.

dt.click: slotProps.toggleItem('{12FC33EC-A725-42D9-B6EE-8ECF0AB90892}','How can I register a complaint about the interview process?')
dt.keyup.enter: slotProps.toggleItem('{12FC33EC-A725-42D9-B6EE-8ECF0AB90892}', 'How can I register a complaint about the interview process?')
dt.h3: How can I register a complaint about the interview process?

div.p: We are committed to an open culture of trust and honest communication, where violations of the Code of Conduct are not tolerated. Anyone can report issues with respect to our Code of Conduct through ASML’s global Speak Up & Non-retaliation Policy. People who speak up will be protected for raising concerns about suspected misconduct in good faith. Reports will be treated confidentially and parties can report concerns anonymously.

dt.click: slotProps.toggleItem('{3701BB41-30E2-4323-B3EB-45C3E60893BF}','How can I identify recruitment fraud?')
dt.keyup.enter: slotProps.toggleItem('{3701BB41-30E2-4323-B3EB-45C3E60893BF}', 'How can I identify recruitment fraud?')
dt.h3: How can I identify recruitment fraud?

dd.div: Scammers may post fraudulent job openings and contact job seekers with fake job offers. They may even conduct fraudulent interviews and attempt to obtain money or personal information. Click here for all the information you need to identify and respond to recruitment fraud.

dt.click: slotProps.toggleItem('{B058E38A-BC06-4155-987E-EDA0A9C0D75D}','Does ASML offer relocation support?')
dt.keyup.enter: slotProps.toggleItem('{B058E38A-BC06-4155-987E-EDA0A9C0D75D}', 'Does ASML offer relocation support?')
dt.h3: Does ASML offer relocation support?

dd.div: If you are an 'international local hire' – in other words, you were hired to work in a different country or state than where you currently live – ASML will support the relocation of you and your direct family members (spouse and children). ASML will provide support for immigration, travel, shipping personal belongings, cultural awareness and language training, and tax advice.

dt.click: slotProps.toggleItem('{A7439755-2600-4BDC-B54F-76888F0D6215}','Can you help my spouse in finding a job as well?')
dt.keyup.enter: slotProps.toggleItem('{A7439755-2600-4BDC-B54F-76888F0D6215}', 'Can you help my spouse in finding a job as well?')
dt.h3: Can you help my spouse in finding a job as well?

dd.div: If your spouse is a good fit for another ASML vacancy, you can both join the ASML referral program.

dt.click: slotProps.toggleItem('{8CF3C1D5-2087-457B-840E-06A6757D99B6}','Does ASML help with continued learning and development?')
dt.keyup.enter: slotProps.toggleItem('{8CF3C1D5-2087-457B-840E-06A6757D99B6}', 'Does ASML help with continued learning and development?')
dt.h3: Does ASML help with continued learning and development?

dd.div: We support lifelong learning for all employees, individually and collectively, across the globe. We do so by offering an appropriate blend of training, on-the-job learning experience and facilitating meaningful connections and collaboration through all parts and layers of the organization. Together with managers who support and Learning & Development that enables, employees are empowered to continuously drive their own development so as to optimally support our business and customers. Our offering covers development in the area of technical skills development, as well as in the area of soft skills and (personal) leadership development.

dt.click: slotProps.toggleItem('{201180D8-1397-4C45-8D13-7B37988C3F3F}','Does ASML offer remote jobs?')
dt.keyup.enter: slotProps.toggleItem('{201180D8-1397-4C45-8D13-7B37988C3F3F}', 'Does ASML offer remote jobs?')
dt.h3: Does ASML offer remote jobs?

div.p: We believe that we share knowledge, innovate and collaborate best when meeting in person, but we recognize that some tasks can be done just as effectively outside the office. ASML’s work-from-home guidelines blend office and remote working, as we believe both have benefits for individuals, the business and the environment.
Working from abroad is generally not permissible due to tax, social security and other implications for both the employee and ASML.

dt.click: slotProps.toggleItem('{20DB1E05-3B08-4F43-9EFD-DB2639971BA5}','How does ASML use my personal data?')
dt.keyup.enter: slotProps.toggleItem('{20DB1E05-3B08-4F43-9EFD-DB2639971BA5}', 'How does ASML use my personal data?')
dt.h3: How does ASML use my personal data?

dd.div: We are committed to respecting and protecting the privacy of our candidates. Any personal data we receive is managed in a professional, lawful and ethical way, in line with our Code of Conduct and in compliance with applicable laws and regulations. Please read our privacy policy for job applicants.

dt.click: slotProps.toggleItem('{92F5671F-A3D4-4F8D-B246-5EF14CA434BA}','How long will ASML keep my personal data?')
dt.keyup.enter: slotProps.toggleItem('{92F5671F-A3D4-4F8D-B246-5EF14CA434BA}', 'How long will ASML keep my personal data?')
dt.h3: How long will ASML keep my personal data?

dd.div: Your data is kept only for the period required for recruitment and compliance purposes. Please read more about how long we keep personal data in our privacy notice for job applicants.

dt.click: slotProps.toggleItem('{2D07768A-F4CE-4C82-9FA1-7FEC9E0AB3BA}','How can I request that my personal data be deleted?')
dt.keyup.enter: slotProps.toggleItem('{2D07768A-F4CE-4C82-9FA1-7FEC9E0AB3BA}', 'How can I request that my personal data be deleted?')
dt.h3: How can I request that my personal data be deleted?

dd.div: You will need to contact the Privacy Office to have your personal data deleted. Please read more about this process in our privacy notice for job applicants.

ul.li: (10/12/2021 yu to all) National Resident Matching Program (NRMP). We implemented the NRMP algorithms which can be used by any discipline or research field to streamline their coordinated hiring processes and maximize the preferences of employers and candidates. Once a match has been set up any job posting can join the match and set up a rank order list with the candidates they have interviewed and want to hire or those they have made contingent offers to. Applicants can accept or decline match assignments, and match can run multiple times if needed. Please let us know if your discipline or field wants to try this feature and we can set up a match for you.

(05/18/2018 yu to all) Integration with your university's recruitment system. Integration with your university's recruitment system. AcademicJobsOnline is designed to be flexible and it works well for search committee members, reference writers and applicants. Our system also allows universities to set up automated processes to synchronize application data with their local databases and to post job ads on our site automatically using a simple API. This way your university can maintain your recruitment data locally, access a large application pool on our system, and allow your faculty to continue using a system they like. Group managers can get more info by selecting "Data Exports" and "Data URLs" from the "Help" menu. Please contact us if your university is interested in using us as a part of your institution-wide recruitment solution and we'll be happy to work with you or your vendors on integration.
